title: DDFP 592: AFC West Preview & Ideal Player-for-Player Trades
itunes:title: DDFP 592: AFC West Preview & Ideal Player-for-Player Trades
description:
Dave Dameshek, Handsome Hank and Matt "Franchise" Franciscovich discuss the best hypothetical player-for-player trades in the NFL in response to the news of Kyrie Irving being traded to the Celtics. Then, the fellas break down the AFC West, predicting how each team will finish within the division. Plus, Shek talks with NFL Films' Keith Cossrow about the current season of Hard Knocks and how the producers find and choose the most compelling stories each week.
